task.en: I want to know the version of the app Voice Memos installed on my mac. Help me navigate to the page that shows this.
task.zh: 我想知道语音备忘录的软件版本。请帮我打开显示其软件版本的界面。
task.ar: أريد معرفة إصدار تطبيق Voice Memos المثبت على جهاز Mac الخاص بي. ساعدني في الانتقال إلى الصفحة التي تعرض هذا.
task.ja: MacにインストールされているVoice Memosアプリのバージョンを知りたいです。その情報が表示されるページへ案内してください。
task.ru: Мне нужно узнать версию приложения Voice Memos, установленного на моём Mac. Помогите открыть страницу, где отображается эта информация.

grading_command: osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "Voice Memos" | grep -q "Version" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "语音备忘录" | grep -q "版本" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "المذكرات الصوتية" | grep -q "الإصدار" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "ボイスメモ" | grep -q "バージョン" && echo "True" || echo "False"

osascript -e 'tell application "System Events" to get value of attribute "AXChildren" of window 1 of (first application process whose frontmost is true)' 2>/dev/null | grep "Диктофон" | grep -q "Версия" && echo "True" || echo "False"
